quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,By the Fig and the Olive
  95,2,And the Mount of Sinai
  95,3,And the City (Makkah) of security —
  95,4,We have truly created man in the best of forms
  95,5,Then We bring him down (to be) the lowest of the low—
  95,6,"Except those who believe and do righteous deeds: For they shall have an unfailing reward"
  95,7,"Then what can be against you (O Prophet!), after this regarding the Judgment (to come)"
  95,8,Is Allah not the Wisest of judges